course.title: Integrative Analysis
course.desc: Integration of the enabling competencies and the six technical competency areas required of a CPA. Developing strategic leadership capabilities and the ability to bring an integrative perspective to decision-making including: professional and ethical behaviour, problem-solving and decision-making, communication (both written and oral), self-management, teamwork and leadership.

block.n: Desautels GCPA Prog students only. Intensive course. Add/drop May 17, w/withdrawal Jun 21.
